                            <ab xml:id="en_91Aaaa001" corresp="#pericope_91Aaaa001" xml:lang="EN">
                                <lb/>If the chair which it is now my honour to inaugurate 
                                <lb/>represented 
                                <lb/>a new discipline in our University,
                                <lb/> if my brief - or my privilege - today was
                                <lb/>to show you the edifice
                                <lb/>which the science of 
                                <lb/>language has been 
                                <lb/>constructing over seventy years, 
                                <lb/>to outline 
