                                <lb/>to define its aim, 
                                <lb/>its use, 
                                <lb/>the mark out the place that
                                <lb/>it occupies in 
                                <lb/>the realm of human knowledge 
                                <lb/>and its possible applications 
                                <lb/>in any Arts faculty, I would be afraid of falling short
                                <lb/>of my task, but I 
                                <lb/>could certainly not
                                <lb/>complain 
                                <lb/>of neglect.
                            </ab>
