                                <lb/>how might
                                <lb/>the discipline benefit,
                                <lb/>classical learning, the knowedge 
                                <lb/>of Greek, Latin, and French,
                                <lb/>even in its purely literary dimension,
                                <lb/>and how might the same subject throw light
                                <lb/>on history or 
                            </ab> 
                        </div>                         
                    </body>
                </text>       
            </group>
        </group>


